  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study is conducted in Europe. The aim of the study is to gather information about
      hypoglycaemia (low blood glucose) among patients with Type 1 or Type 2 diabetes mellitus.
      The study is both retrospective and prospective.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
